---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Live demo — link-out to WordPress Playground (matches WC/WP/Cart sales-site pattern).
// Blueprint at /public/playground/blueprint.json installs WC + Storefront + Asteris Affiliates
// then activates with dev-mode (no licence needed inside the sandbox).
const PLAYGROUND_URL = 'https://playground.wordpress.net/?blueprint-url=https://asterisaffiliates.com/playground/blueprint.json';
---
<Layout seoSlug="/demo">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">★ LIVE IN YOUR BROWSER</div>
      <h1>Try Asteris Affiliates.<br /><span class="accent">No install. No signup.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">
        A full WordPress + WooCommerce + Asteris Affiliates store, running entirely in your browser via <strong>WordPress Playground</strong>. All 23 features enabled. Click around, approve a test affiliate, watch a commission credit in real time.
      </p>
      <p class="boot">First-time boot takes ~30–60 seconds while Playground spins up WordPress + WooCommerce + Asteris Affiliates.</p>
      <div class="hactions">
        <a href={PLAYGROUND_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-pop btn-large">★ Launch the Playground demo →</a>
        <a href="/free" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">Or install Asteris Free →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="status">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <div class="sbox">
        <div class="seye">★ LIVE DEMO — ALL 23 FEATURES PRE-ACTIVATED</div>
        <p>The Playground blueprint installs WordPress + WooCommerce + Storefront, then fetches the latest Asteris Affiliates zip directly from this site and activates it with every feature on in dev-mode (no licence key needed inside the sandbox). First boot takes 30–60 seconds — subsequent boots are cached.</p>
        <p>Want it on your own store instead? <a href="/free">Grab Asteris Affiliates Free</a> on WordPress.org (when published) or <a href="/pricing">see paid pricing</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="active">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What's active in the demo</h2>
      <p class="csub">5 sample affiliates, 30 days of commission history, pending payouts in queue. The Playground demo loads straight into the WP admin so you can approve, suspend, and explore every feature.</p>
      <div class="agrid">
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Admin side</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Dashboard widget with 30-day commission totals</li>
            <li>5 sample affiliates with mixed approval states</li>
            <li>30 days of commission history with realistic mix</li>
            <li>Pending payout batch ready to run (simulated)</li>
            <li>Affiliate onboarding wizard (4 steps)</li>
            <li>Admin impersonation ("View as Sarah")</li>
            <li>Per-product commission rates (3 sample products)</li>
            <li>Two-tier (MLM) toggle in Settings</li>
            <li>AI swipe-copy library (16 seed snippets)</li>
            <li>A/B email tests with sample results</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="acol">
          <h3>Affiliate side</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Front-end affiliate portal (mobile-responsive)</li>
            <li>Vanity <code>/go/sarah</code> landing pages</li>
            <li>Stats dashboard with charts</li>
            <li>Referral link generator</li>
            <li>Swipe-copy browser + copy-to-clipboard</li>
            <li>Payout history + next-payout estimate</li>
            <li>Profile + payout method editor</li>
            <li>Sample storefront with test products</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="limits">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>What works in Playground vs what doesn't</h2>
      <div class="lgrid">
        <div class="lcol works">
          <h3>★ Works</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Full WordPress + WooCommerce admin</li>
            <li>Approving / suspending affiliates</li>
            <li>Browsing the storefront + using affiliate links</li>
            <li>Generating test orders that credit commissions</li>
            <li>Enabling MLM tier-2 + seeing parent commissions credit</li>
            <li>Configuring every plugin setting</li>
            <li>Browsing 16 swipe-copy snippets</li>
            <li>Running CSV exports + bulk actions</li>
            <li>Using WP-CLI commands via the Playground console</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lcol limited">
          <h3>★ Limited / unavailable</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>AI swipe-copy variants need your own AI provider key (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.)</li>
            <li>No real PayPal / Stripe API calls (auto-payout simulated only)</li>
            <li>Cloud-assist fraud sync disabled (no contribution from sandbox)</li>
            <li>No real outbound email — written to Tools → Mail log instead</li>
            <li>No persistent storage — close the tab and everything resets</li>
            <li>Licence key not required inside the sandbox (dev-mode)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="after">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>After the demo.</h2>
      <p>Asteris Affiliates Free has 4 core features (tracking, commissions, manual payouts, affiliate portal) and is on WordPress.org. Install it on your store and see how it works with your theme + cart plugin before purchasing.</p>
      <div class="aactions">
        <a href="/free" class="btn btn-large">Get Asteris Affiliates Free →</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline btn-large">See paid pricing →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 36px; }
  .narrow { max-width: 820px; }

  .hero { padding: 80px 0 48px; }
  .hero .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--c-mint);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 80px); line-height: 0.98; letter-spacing: -2px; font-weight: 900; margin: 0 0 28px; }
  .hero h1 .accent { background: linear-gradient(transparent 55%, rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.35) 55%); padding: 0 4px; }
  .hero .lead { font-size: 19px; max-width: 760px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .hero .lead strong { color: var(--c-text); font-weight: 700; }
  .hero .boot { font-size: 14px; color: var(--c-muted); margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .hactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .status { padding: 32px 0; background: rgba(6, 214, 160, 0.12); }
  .sbox { background: var(--c-white); border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px 24px; }
  .seye { color: var(--c-mint); font-weight: 800; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sbox p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sbox a { color: var(--c-mint); text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600; }

  .active { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-white); border-top: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--c-text); }
  .active h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .csub { font-size: 16px; color: var(--c-muted); max-width: 760px; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .agrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .acol h3 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--c-mint); }
  .acol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .acol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 15px; color: var(--c-text); }
  .acol li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--c-mint); font-weight: 700; }
  .acol code { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.06); padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .agrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .limits { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-bg); }
  .limits h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.2px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .lgrid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; }
  .lcol { border: 2px solid var(--c-text); border-radius: 8px; padding: 22px; background: var(--c-white); }
  .works h3 { color: #1a7f37; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .limited h3 { color: #c0392b; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .lcol ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .lcol li { padding: 6px 0 6px 22px; position: relative; font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--c-text); line-height: 1.5; }
  .works li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #1a7f37; font-weight: 800; }
  .limited li::before { content: '⚠'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #c0392b; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .lgrid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .after { padding: 80px 0; background: var(--c-text); color: var(--c-white); text-align: center; border-top: 6px solid var(--c-mint); }
  .after h2 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 42px); font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1.5px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #fff; }
  .after p { font-size: 17px; color: #ccc; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto 24px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .aactions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .after .btn { background: var(--c-mint); border-color: var(--c-mint); color: var(--c-text); }
  .after .btn-outline { background: var(--c-white); color: var(--c-text); border-color: var(--c-white); }
</style>
